svg.source: Title: Guest Adds Gift Ideas Guest-->User Interface: Guest click Events Invitations List User Interface-->Server API: Calls get guest events API Server API-->Database: Read guest events Database-->Server API: Events List Server API-->User Interface: Events List json User Interface-->Guest: Display Page with list of events user is invited as guest Guest-->User Interface: Select an event to edit gift ideas User Interface-->Server API: Calls get gift ideas details API Server API-->Database: Reads gifts ideas for event Database-->Server API: Gifts idea Server API-->User Interface: Gifts ideas json User Interface-->Guest: Display page with gifts ideas Guest-->User Interface: Edit ideas Guest-->User Interface: Search for ideas User Interface-->Server API: Call search gifts API Server API-->Amazon: Search gifts Server API-->User Interface: List of products User Interface-->Guest: Display gifts results Guest-->User Interface: Pick one or more gifts Guest-->User Interface: Save gifts ideas User Interface-->User Interface: Validates Data Note right of User Interface: If error, display message User Interface-->Server API: Calls Save gifts ideas Server API-->Server API: Validates Data Note right of Server API: If error, return with error Server API-->Database: Save gifts ideas Database-->Server API: Saved gifts ideas Server API-->Email Platform: Send email to gifting guest with ideas details Server API-->User Interface: Success result User Interface-->User Interface: Show success message
